      "comment_id" : 38590285,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I disagree with &quot;All references pointing to same object and your program will misbehave.&quot; The only problem is that what happens to the object of one reference happens to the object of another reference -- because it&#39;s the same object. This isn&#39;t misbehaviour; it&#39;s how Java works."
