    "creation_date" : 1439168007,
    "answer_id" : 31910261,
    "question_id" : 6202818,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can do this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String one, two, three = two = one = \"\";\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>But these will all point to the same instance. It won't cause problems with final variables or primitive types. This way, you can do everything in one line.</p>\n"
